Chief to the new driver:
- What's your last name? I only address drivers by their last name!
Driver:
- Andrew!
Chief:
Is that a surname?
Driver:
- That's the name.
Chief:
- You didn't hear me, I need your last name!
Driver:
- Call me by my first name. Andrey!
Chef:
- Why are you so stupid? Tell me your last name!
Driver:
My last name, My Love.
The boss:
- Well, let's go, Andrey.
